versions.title: Version Five
versions.body: React Router DOM enables you to implement dynamic routing in a web app. Unlike the traditional routing architecture in which the routing is handled in a configuration outside of a running app, React Router DOM facilitates component-based routing according to the needs of the app and platform.

versions.title: Version Six
versions.body: The next major version of React Router, version 6, is just around the corner. We published the first alpha release back in January, and we released another alpha last week.
